                  "type": "STRING",
                  "value": "TPR: Thermal Plastic Rubber. TPR is a type of thermoplastic rubber, and thermoplastic is a type of plastic that thanks to its chemical properties, is a flexible and moldable material. Corresponds to the sole of the shoe."
